00:49:15,210 --> 00:49:20,880
Are you saying an attorney will defend that girl who committed the murder?

524
00:49:20,880 --> 00:49:23,140
What? Defend?

525
00:49:23,140 --> 00:49:27,700
Are you saying you will file a lawsuit?

526
00:49:27,700 --> 00:49:32,150
Yes. We will reveal the inside story of this incident through a trial and let the village knowâ€”

527
00:49:32,150 --> 00:49:34,420
Inside story?

528
00:49:34,420 --> 00:49:38,000
With the hoe that girl wielded in broad daylight,

529
00:49:38,000 --> 00:49:40,920
one of the village's elderly was stabbed to death!

530
00:49:40,920 --> 00:49:44,520
What inside story for an incident that is so clearly laid out in front of us?

531
00:49:44,520 --> 00:49:47,420
We should listen to what this new bride has to say as well.

532
00:49:48,740 --> 00:49:52,350
I do not know what amazing inside story there is to tell,

533
00:49:52,350 --> 00:49:56,360
but the fact that girl committed the murder does not change.

534
00:49:56,360 --> 00:49:59,540
We are not trying to hide or change that fact.

535
00:49:59,540 --> 00:50:04,020
It is the process laid out by national law.

536
00:50:04,810 --> 00:50:07,040
National law?

537
00:50:10,010 --> 00:50:13,540
Do you see Joseon anywhere around here?

538
00:50:13,540 --> 00:50:14,990
Pardon?

539
00:50:14,990 --> 00:50:17,780
As you can see, this Dabok-ri

540
00:50:17,780 --> 00:50:21,050
does not receive any food from the government since we do not yield any grain.

541
00:50:21,050 --> 00:50:24,980
- Any important...
 - I heard it so much that I have a scab in my ear.

542
00:50:24,980 --> 00:50:27,070
And we are not even a strategic area, so

543
00:50:27,070 --> 00:50:31,030
we do not even have a military base that is so commonplace.

544
00:50:32,290 --> 00:50:33,120
Yes.

545
00:50:33,120 --> 00:50:35,990
The government that was nowhere to be seen while we suffered through

546
00:50:35,990 --> 00:50:38,450
all kinds of diseases and natural disasters.

547
00:50:38,450 --> 00:50:41,890
The Joseon that showed up only when it was time to collect taxes!

548
00:50:41,890 --> 00:50:45,670
What right does it have to ask us to be fair!

549
00:50:46,790 --> 00:50:48,520
- That is becauseâ€” 
 - That's right!

550
00:50:48,520 --> 00:50:50,960
While the lawsuit is going on, our villagers

551
00:50:50,970 --> 00:50:54,970
