567
00:51:39,760 --> 00:51:43,770
- Money?
 - By chance, did you already accept the settlement?

568
00:51:43,770 --> 00:51:45,420
Well...

569
00:51:49,070 --> 00:51:53,420
I heard your older brother already took the money.

570
00:51:57,430 --> 00:51:58,940
Let us go. Hurry.

571
00:51:58,940 --> 00:52:01,650
Let us hurry!

572
00:52:01,650 --> 00:52:04,660
- Just a moment.
 - Step aside!

573
00:52:05,660 --> 00:52:07,120
What do we do? Just let them go?

574
00:52:07,120 --> 00:52:08,570
What can you do?

575
00:52:08,570 --> 00:52:10,550
They already took the money.

576
00:52:10,550 --> 00:52:13,300
How can we defeat money?

577
00:52:13,300 --> 00:52:15,960
This is unbelievable.

578
00:52:29,260 --> 00:52:30,900
Hands up.

579
00:52:45,590 --> 00:52:48,690
Consider yourselves lucky that we are ending it like this.

580
00:52:48,690 --> 00:52:51,230
Don't you dare come back to our village again!

581
00:52:51,230 --> 00:52:53,870
If you do, I will just!

582
00:52:55,890 --> 00:52:57,880
Geez! Let us go.

583
00:53:04,860 --> 00:53:07,840
Whoa, this is so unbelievable.

584
00:53:07,840 --> 00:53:11,320
I know! How could they do this to innocent outsiders?

585
00:53:11,320 --> 00:53:14,610
