635
00:56:30,320 --> 00:56:32,670
When was your last period?

636
00:56:32,670 --> 00:56:35,010
Was it in the last month?

637
00:56:37,160 --> 00:56:40,400
- Mom, what do I do? 
 - Oh, my.

638
00:56:40,400 --> 00:56:42,690
What do I do?

639
00:56:44,250 --> 00:56:47,140
What do you mean what do you do?

640
00:56:50,450 --> 00:56:52,510
Mom!

641
00:56:52,510 --> 00:56:54,950
I want to live!

642
00:56:54,950 --> 00:56:57,900
Of course. You must live.

643
00:56:57,900 --> 00:57:01,120
You are leaving here so you can live.

644
00:57:01,120 --> 00:57:05,310
Go somewhere and cultivate some wastelandâ€”

645
00:57:05,310 --> 00:57:07,130
Not like that.

646
00:57:07,130 --> 00:57:08,760
I want to live properly,

647
00:57:08,760 --> 00:57:11,050
