648
00:57:11,050 --> 00:57:12,790
Darling...

649
00:57:13,520 --> 00:57:15,630
I want to file a lawsuit.

650
00:57:15,630 --> 00:57:19,080
I will go through trial, pay for my crime,

651
00:57:19,080 --> 00:57:21,050
and live my life properly afterward.

652
00:57:21,050 --> 00:57:23,440
If you go through a trial, you will die!

653
00:57:23,440 --> 00:57:25,510
Have you seen anyone who lived after killing a person?

654
00:57:25,510 --> 00:57:27,500
He said he could save me.

655
00:57:27,500 --> 00:57:30,720
That attorney said there is a way I could survive.

656
00:57:30,720 --> 00:57:32,440
How could you believe that?

657
00:57:32,440 --> 00:57:34,780
It is nothing more than gambling with your life.

658
00:57:34,780 --> 00:57:39,640
I do not want my child to live in hiding all his life because of me.

659
00:57:39,640 --> 00:57:43,280
When he's grown up, he'll have to get married as well.

660
00:57:46,450 --> 00:57:50,270
But what can we do now?

661
00:57:51,020 --> 00:57:53,780
We even received all the settlement money.

662
00:57:53,780 --> 00:57:56,180
We can give it back.

663
00:57:56,180 --> 00:57:58,880
Where is Orabeoni right now?

664
00:58:01,530 --> 00:58:03,680
Mom!

665
00:58:04,660 --> 00:58:08,000
No. I cannot tell you.

666
00:58:08,000 --> 00:58:10,730
Your brother needs to live, too.

667
00:58:11,860 --> 00:58:14,330
You will end up...

668
00:58:17,400 --> 00:58:19,460
End up...

669
00:58:20,250 --> 00:58:21,720
What?

670
00:58:23,100 --> 00:58:26,460
- Aigoo... 
- I'm hopeless anyway.

671
00:58:26,460 --> 00:58:29,520
That I will end up dying anyway?

672
00:58:31,510 --> 00:58:34,320
Aigoo. Yeong Sil!

673
00:58:34,320 --> 00:58:38,380
Mom. You don't trust me.

674
00:58:38,380 --> 00:58:41,010
What he said about me surviving this.

675
00:58:42,020 --> 00:58:45,960
No. You don't want me to live.

676
00:58:45,960 --> 00:58:50,030
- You want me to die, do you not? 
- No!

677
00:58:50,030 --> 00:58:53,240
Yeong Sil! Child!

678
00:59:43,070 --> 00:59:45,720
Where are those people?

679
00:59:45,720 --> 00:59:48,170
Who do you mean?

680
00:59:48,170 --> 00:59:50,320
The secret royal inspector.

681
00:59:50,320 --> 00:59:52,720
He asked where the jade dragon came from

682
00:59:52,720 --> 00:59:57,140
