695
01:00:47,890 --> 01:00:50,420
Did the rumor spread already?

696
01:00:50,420 --> 01:00:55,790
Something like my guys turned the village upside down?

697
01:01:01,190 --> 01:01:05,350
Looking at the number of shoes, you have at least one empty room.

698
01:01:08,650 --> 01:01:13,840
Seeing how the kitchen is filled with smoke, you're in the middle of cooking.

699
01:01:17,670 --> 01:01:20,360
Whether you all sleep in one room or not, I don't care.

700
01:01:20,360 --> 01:01:23,630
I am tired, so feed yourselves.

701
01:01:23,630 --> 01:01:25,720
We will do so.

702
01:02:10,800 --> 01:02:12,510
You are hot because you are standing next to the furnace.

703
01:02:12,510 --> 01:02:14,640
