737
01:05:53,440 --> 01:05:55,720
Jeong Wol.

738
01:05:55,800 --> 01:05:58,200
Come here.

739
01:05:58,200 --> 01:06:00,890
Come, come.

740
01:06:01,810 --> 01:06:04,720
Gosh, scared me!

